  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ 475ºF/ Gas 9</p>\n<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chickpeas</strong> and <strong>ground cumin</strong> to a tray, drizzle with<strong> olive oil </strong>and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>\n<p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 20-25 min or until starting to crisp</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">While the chickpeas are cooking, peel</span> and grate (or crush) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Lato;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;\"> </span></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>free from <span class=\"text-highlight\">mayonnaise</span></strong>, <strong>grated garlic </strong>(<span class=\"text-highlight\">don't</span> like raw garlic? Go easy!) and <strong>dried oregano</strong> in a small bowl </p>\n<p>Add a 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Stir it all together –</span> this is your <strong>garlic<span class=\"text-highlight\"> &amp;</span> herb mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
