            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1790.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Separate out the larger outer <strong>little gem leaves</strong> and finely shred the inner core</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>cucumber</strong> into discs then cut each disc into matchsticks </p>\n<p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly</p>\n<p>Dice the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Slice the <strong>black olives</strong> finely</p>",
